Rating: 3
Loved the fact that it is simply a few ingredients and 275 calories a serving, 5 grams of fat. You can substitute turkey bacon or uncured bacon for a healthier option. I agree that there was too much sauce and like the idea of adding the tomatoes and adding the juice afterwards. I also added fresh tomatoes to the sauté and a little white wine cooked down. Husband loved the smell as he walked through the door.

